title: Workspace 1_002.jpg
description:
Thought I would just update with the latest progress for AppIndicator support for budgie-remix ... looking good!

This is my default working set (left to right)

Variety, Redshift, Qtorrent, VirtualBox Indicator, GIS Weather, ClipIt, Shutter, Radio Tray.

Can confirm My-Weather-Indicator works nicely. NoNotification appindicator doesn't through - this is Unity specific.

AppIndicators works very nicely side-by-side with the system tray. Best for all applications.
